Class FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.NeighbourSelectionWithContext<Lecture,Placement,FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourSelection.FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourContext>
      • org.cpsolver.coursett.heuristics.FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanHoldContext, HasAssignmentContext<Lecture,Placement,FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourSelection.FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourContext>, NeighbourSelection<Lecture,Placement>

    public class FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourSelection
extends NeighbourSelectionWithContext<Lecture,Placement,FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourSelection.FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourContext>
    University course timetabling neighbour selection.

    When a complete solution is found, it is improved by limited depth backtracking search. This way it is ensured that the fund solution is at least locally optimal.
    Version:
    CourseTT 1.3 (University Course Timetabling)
